}}&lt;/ref&gt; Hopefully we can replace this with a reputable pundit (not a tabloid)--&gt; In the second innings he added an unbeaten 22 from 119 balls, but England collapsed to 129 all out and so went 2&amp;ndash;0 down.&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web
