Despite the series ending with a 5&amp;ndash;0 whitewash by Australia,&lt;!-- the first since 1921?--&gt; Collingwood finished the series ranked 14th in the LG ICC World Rankings for Test batsmen.&lt;ref&gt;{{Cite web
