=== One-Day Internationals ===
'''Records:'''
* Most capped ODI player for England&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web |url=http://stats.cricinfo.com/ci/engine/records/batting/most_runs_career.html?class=2;id=1;type=team|title=Records / England / One-Day Internationals /  Most runs|publisher=CricInfo|accessdate=22 October 2009}}&lt;/ref&gt;
* Best bowling figures in an ODI by an England player &amp;ndash; 6/31 against [[Bangladeshi cricket team|Bangladesh]] in 2005.&lt;ref name=best_bowling_eng_odi/&gt;&lt;ref name=best_all_round_odi&gt;{{citeweb
| url = http://www.cricketarchive.com/Archive/Scorecards/82/82675.html
| title = 6/31 &amp; 112* vs Bangladesh
| accessdate = 17 February 2007
}}&lt;/ref&gt;
* Best ODI all-round performance - 6/31 and 112* against [[Bangladeshi cricket team|Bangladesh]] in 2005.&lt;ref name=first_100runs_6wickets/&gt;&lt;ref name=best_all_round_odi/&gt;
* Fastest half century by an England player, 50 off 24 deliveries.&lt;ref&gt;[http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/cricket/england/7254200.stm ''New Zealand v England one-day series''] [[BBC News]] retrieved 20 February 2008&lt;/ref&gt;
* The most career runs in ODI matches for England.&lt;ref name=&quot;odiruns&quot;/&gt;
